\begin_layout Section
Introduction
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
VizStack is a visualization management software written in Python.
 It can be used to manage a visualization cluster, a bunch of visualization
 nodes (sea of nodes) and individual graphic enabled SMP servers.
 This documentation covers installation, configuration and operation of
 VizStack.
\end_layout

