\begin_layout Standard
VizStack is the management software which manages visualization resources.
 This manual assumes that either RHEL5 and Suse 10.2 Linux is already installed
 on the machine(s).
 VizStack does not provide any capabilites for cluster managment.
 The installation, configuration and image propagation should already be
 completed before starting the installation of VizStack.
 Please refer to the manual of the cluster managment suite for these tasks.
